@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jnfpod(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.80) / v2) + wp.sin(0.18))
    tmp = (0.38 * v1)
    v0 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.09) * tmp) - tmp)
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = (((v0 + 0.43 + v1 + 0.89) * v0) * wp.sin((v2 + 0.53 * v1 + 0.09)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.abs(v0 + 0.87)))
    data[tid] = v0
